%% C4 dynamic — Replay / audit of past events for a workflow
%% Source of truth: docs/adr/ + docs/architecture-brief.md — regenerate via /c4-designer, do not hand-edit
%% Generated: 2026-07-10
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant OP as Operator
    participant CLI as CLI
    participant SRV as byteswarm Server
    participant BUS as Event Bus

    OP->>CLI: replay workflow workflowID [shell]
    CLI->>SRV: request replay(workflowID, from = seq/time) [JSON/HTTPS]
    SRV->>BUS: open replay consumer from sequence/time on stream [NATS]
    loop each retained event for workflowID
        BUS-->>SRV: deliver past event [NATS]
        SRV->>SRV: re-dispatch to consumers (idempotent)
    end
    SRV-->>CLI: replay complete (event count) [JSON/HTTPS]
    CLI-->>OP: summary [shell]
